<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 08:10:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡不再控制以色列的事态发展——这让他心烦意乱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-no-longer-controls-events-in-israel-and-its-driving-him-to-distraction/00000190-5b17-def3-a5b6-db37f5d80000</link><description>以色列最高法院关于正统派征兵豁免的裁决可能会产生改变现实的影响 ■ 如果还有人有任何疑问，本周情况变得更加明确：内塔尼亚胡不会同意就 10 月 7 日的灾难成立调查委员会 ■ 以色列是否已经通过了“法国法”，尽管议会还没有通过它？</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 03:03:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-no-longer-controls-events-in-israel-and-its-driving-him-to-distraction/00000190-5b17-def3-a5b6-db37f5d80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡正在发动三场消耗战：针对哈马斯、真主党和以色列人民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-three-wars-of-attrition-against-hamas-hezbollah-and-the-israeli-people/00000190-5af8-d1c4-affa-5bfee2a50000</link><description>以色列总理希望他的人民继续处于不确定性的迷雾中，使他们更加依赖功能失调的政府 ■ 与真主党爆发全面战争的可能性似乎比几天前要小 — — 但这并不意味着敌对行动已经结束 ■ 以色列国防军正在适应新的战斗强度不断变化的惯例</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 03:02:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-three-wars-of-attrition-against-hamas-hezbollah-and-the-israeli-people/00000190-5af8-d1c4-affa-5bfee2a50000</guid></item><item><title>“当人们听说我要去以色列时，他们会感到不安”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-06-28/ty-article/.highlight/when-people-hear-that-im-going-to-israel-they-get-upset/00000190-5c98-d7e5-a1f3-dd990d5b0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一位美国犹太人前往以色列三天，第一次见到她的团队成员，两位七十多岁的姐妹回忆起她们在爱情方面做出的选择</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 02:36:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-06-28/ty-article/.highlight/when-people-hear-that-im-going-to-israel-they-get-upset/00000190-5c98-d7e5-a1f3-dd990d5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方公布在加沙战斗中丧生的士兵姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article-live/smotrich-backtracks-on-decision-to-withhold-funds-from-pa-fearing-its-collapse/00000190-5c9f-d7e5-a1f3-dd9ff3360000</link><description>以色列国防军在加沙市舒贾亚附近启动基于情报的行动；加沙人报告有 30 人死亡、数十人受伤 ■ 斯莫特里奇因担心巴勒斯坦权力机构崩溃而取消了扣留巴勒斯坦权力机构资金的决定 ■ 以色列军队表示，从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射的 40 枚火箭弹，其中一半被拦截 ■ 安全部门表示，美国敦促公民“强烈重新考虑”黎巴嫩旅行情况可能会很快“改变”</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 02:23:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article-live/smotrich-backtracks-on-decision-to-withhold-funds-from-pa-fearing-its-collapse/00000190-5c9f-d7e5-a1f3-dd9ff3360000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：“我们拯救了以色列”；特朗普：“他变得像巴勒斯坦人”：首场总统辩论中的灾难性表现与不断的谎言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/biden-trump-clash-over-israel-iran-and-antisemitism-at-first-president-debate/00000190-5c8b-dc65-abff-7cabf5ef0000</link><description>特朗普第一个提到以色列，攻击拜登的外交政策，并重申哈马斯永远不会在他的领导下袭击以色列。拜登坚称，他的政府一直站在以色列一边，并补充说，“我们正在为以色列提供他们需要的所有武器，并在他们需要时提供”</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 02:05:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/biden-trump-clash-over-israel-iran-and-antisemitism-at-first-president-debate/00000190-5c8b-dc65-abff-7cabf5ef0000</guid></item><item><title>我的特拉维夫邻居对我很好。原来他是敌人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.highlight/my-tel-aviv-neighbor-has-been-nothing-but-nice-to-me-turns-out-hes-the-enemy/00000190-5c61-d506-ab9a-7c6b54df0000</link><description>旷日持久的战争的影响之一就是摘掉了那些自以为可以共同生活的人们的所有面具。差距正在扩大，而且似乎已经结束</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 02:04:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.highlight/my-tel-aviv-neighbor-has-been-nothing-but-nice-to-me-turns-out-hes-the-enemy/00000190-5c61-d506-ab9a-7c6b54df0000</guid></item><item><title>“毫无疑问，以色列的政变正在发生”：最高法院法官阿纳特·巴伦的惊人警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israels-coup-is-alive-and-kicking-a-stunning-warning-by-justice-anat-baron/00000190-5b0a-dc65-abff-7b2b72f50000</link><description>10 月 7 日后几天从最高法院退休的阿纳特·巴伦 (Anat Baron) 法官表示，以色列正处于最低点；在这个戏剧性的时刻，她觉得自己没有权利保持沉默</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 01:04:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israels-coup-is-alive-and-kicking-a-stunning-warning-by-justice-anat-baron/00000190-5b0a-dc65-abff-7b2b72f50000</guid></item><item><title>加拿大对西岸著名的以色列定居者领导人和组织实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/canada-imposes-sanctions-on-prominent-israeli-settler-leaders-organizations-in-west-bank/00000190-5ac4-d63a-a7b2-5fdf96230000</link><description>加拿大是第一个制裁约旦河西岸主要定居点组织阿马纳的政府，该组织表示其目标是在约旦河西岸安置 100 万定居者</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 18:16:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/canada-imposes-sanctions-on-prominent-israeli-settler-leaders-organizations-in-west-bank/00000190-5ac4-d63a-a7b2-5fdf96230000</guid></item><item><title>拜登与特朗普的辩论将是美国对以色列战争的前所未有的展示</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-27/ty-article/.highlight/biden-trump-debate-will-be-an-unprecedented-display-of-americas-wars-over-israel/00000190-590a-def3-a5b6-db2f35450000</link><description>以色列或反犹太主义很少成为美国总统辩论的核心问题。这一次，他们很可能扮演主角，尽管有些不和谐</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 17:26:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-27/ty-article/.highlight/biden-trump-debate-will-be-an-unprecedented-display-of-americas-wars-over-israel/00000190-590a-def3-a5b6-db2f35450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 265 天：监管机构警告称，以色列不准备在发生战争时从北部撤离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-265-israel-not-ready-to-evacuate-north-in-case-of-war-watchdog-warns/00000190-5a95-def3-a5b6-dab7b76b0001</link><description>美国官员警告以色列，即使在黎巴嫩南部进行有限的地面行动也可能导致与伊朗的地区战争 ■ 居民告诉《国土报》，以色列国防军猛烈轰炸加沙城 Zeitoun 社区 Shujaiyeh ■ 美国、德国和荷兰警告其公民不要前往黎巴嫩 ■ 三据报道，以色列在大马士革以南发动的袭击中丧生 ■ 战争进入 265 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 16:50:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-265-israel-not-ready-to-evacuate-north-in-case-of-war-watchdog-warns/00000190-5a95-def3-a5b6-dab7b76b0001</guid></item><item><title>人质和10月7日受害者家属请愿以色列最高法院成立调查委员会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/hostages-and-oct-7-victims-families-petition-high-court-establish-commission-of-inquiry/00000190-59f9-d63a-a7b2-5dff68f90000</link><description>“负责以色列公众福祉的人们必须为自己在这场灾难中所扮演的角色承担责任”：请愿者要求调查委员会调查导致 10 月 7 日哈马斯致命袭击的原因</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 16:36:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/hostages-and-oct-7-victims-families-petition-high-court-establish-commission-of-inquiry/00000190-59f9-d63a-a7b2-5dff68f90000</guid></item><item><title>美国警告以色列：即使是有限的南黎巴嫩演习也可能导致真主党与伊朗战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/u-s-warns-israel-even-limited-south-lebanon-maneuver-could-lead-to-hezbollah-iran-war/00000190-59d2-d506-ab9a-79fa5e310000</link><description>一名美国官员在最近与以色列国防官员会面时表示，即使以色列发誓只想将真主党赶出边境，而不想摧毁贝鲁特，对方也可能不会相信。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 15:57:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/u-s-warns-israel-even-limited-south-lebanon-maneuver-could-lead-to-hezbollah-iran-war/00000190-59d2-d506-ab9a-79fa5e310000</guid></item><item><title>令人眼花缭乱的速度，然后下降：美国对以色列的武器运输如何放缓</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/a-dizzying-pace-then-a-drop-how-u-s-arms-shipments-to-israel-slowed-down/00000190-59b6-dc65-abff-79bff9b10000</link><description>公开的航班跟踪数据显示，自加沙战争爆发以来，每个月有多少美国武器抵达以色列，交付速度急剧上升，然后逐渐放缓</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 15:17:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/a-dizzying-pace-then-a-drop-how-u-s-arms-shipments-to-israel-slowed-down/00000190-59b6-dc65-abff-79bff9b10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院命令本-格维尔部披露有关非法发放枪支许可证的信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/court-orders-ben-gvirs-ministry-to-disclose-info-about-unlawful-issuance-of-gun-licenses/00000190-59f9-def3-a5b6-dbffac870000</link><description>以色列法院命令极右翼议员伊塔马尔·本·格维尔领导的国家安全部向调查人员提供与他的雇员非法分发枪支许可证有关的文件。警方消息人士称，调查被推迟是因为担心这会导致对本-格维尔本人的怀疑</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 15:16:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/court-orders-ben-gvirs-ministry-to-disclose-info-about-unlawful-issuance-of-gun-licenses/00000190-59f9-def3-a5b6-dbffac870000</guid></item><item><title>“没有出路”：以色列 80 年代流行歌星亚当去世</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-80s-pop-star-adam-dies/00000190-59d8-de5e-abd0-fbfac8f70000</link><description>Adam 是 80 年代和 90 年代初最伟大的以色列流行偶像之一。他在遗言中说道：“我感谢这一生的美好旅程。”他要求在死后发表遗言。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:45:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-80s-pop-star-adam-dies/00000190-59d8-de5e-abd0-fbfac8f70000</guid></item><item><title>“回家”：耶路撒冷博物馆鼓动犹太人“征服并定居”整个加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/visiting-the-jerusalem-museum-that-agitates-for-jews-to-conquer-and-settle-all-of-gaza/00000190-58a9-ddd9-a1f1-dafbe4b80000</link><description>古什卡蒂夫博物馆是一个由极右翼拉比和前定居者建立的“非政治性”私人企业，它的时间远没有被冻结：战争期间，其收藏的烛台被以色列国防军士兵“征用”在加沙点燃，而博物馆导游侮辱阿拉伯人，并对加沙和黎巴嫩南部的新定居点感到兴奋</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:44:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/visiting-the-jerusalem-museum-that-agitates-for-jews-to-conquer-and-settle-all-of-gaza/00000190-58a9-ddd9-a1f1-dafbe4b80000</guid></item><item><title>萨拉·内塔尼亚胡呼吁美国第一夫人要求无条件释放以色列国防军女观察员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/sara-netanyahu-calls-on-first-lady-to-demand-unconditional-release-of-idf-female-spotters/00000190-59a9-ddd9-a1f1-dbfb50fd0000</link><description>在给吉尔·拜登的第二封信中，总理夫人要求第一夫人与她和观察者的母亲一起领导一个联盟，推动将女孩从哈马斯的囚禁中解救出来。此举是内塔尼亚胡与人质家属之间有些坎坷的关系的一部分</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:03:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/sara-netanyahu-calls-on-first-lady-to-demand-unconditional-release-of-idf-female-spotters/00000190-59a9-ddd9-a1f1-dbfb50fd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列悲伤专家：“我们不区分加沙儿童和哈马斯努赫巴部队”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-dont-distinguish-between-a-child-in-gaza-and-hamas-nukhba-force/00000190-4a6f-da60-a5b7-cfef76da0000</link><description>自战争开始以来，心理健康专家兼作家梅拉夫·罗斯（Yair Lapid 的妹妹兼红颜知己）一直在治疗人们的创伤。现在她担心灾难对社会造成的后果：“报复每个人的愿望对我们来说非常危险”</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 13:33:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-dont-distinguish-between-a-child-in-gaza-and-hamas-nukhba-force/00000190-4a6f-da60-a5b7-cfef76da0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队暂停在反政府抗议活动中被拘留的士兵的预备役义务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-suspends-reserve-duty-for-soldiers-detained-at-anti-government-protests/00000190-590c-ddd9-a1f1-dbfe96960000</link><description>据军方称，在收到警方报告后，预备役军人的服役将暂时停止，直至案件审理结束，并且预备役军人可以对决定提出上诉。 “我不敢相信这会自动发生，”一名被停职的预备役军人阿隆·格鲁佐夫 (Alon Gruzov) 说道，他在一次抗议活动中挡住了臭鼬水炮。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 13:27:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-suspends-reserve-duty-for-soldiers-detained-at-anti-government-protests/00000190-590c-ddd9-a1f1-dbfe96960000</guid></item><item><title>荷兰外交部召见以色列大使澄清涉嫌对国际刑事法院检察官进行间谍活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/netherlands-summons-israeli-ambassador-to-clarify-alleged-spying-of-icc-prosecutors/00000190-5971-d63a-a7b2-5d7f66690000</link><description>在对以色列近十年来对国际刑事法院及其官员进行秘密监视的调查公布后，该部发言人表示，几名荷兰议员对这些指控表示了担忧</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 13:21:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/netherlands-summons-israeli-ambassador-to-clarify-alleged-spying-of-icc-prosecutors/00000190-5971-d63a-a7b2-5d7f66690000</guid></item></channel></rss>